data.description: Property features 2 homes on 26+ acres. with amazing views, over half a mile of road frontage and easy highway access!Main house features full height, dual pane windows, new roof, appliances, and 440' well. Enjoy Low/no cost utilities, heat with new wood burning fireplace insert and cool with solar powered Central HVAC! 10kw solar system connected to PG&E, let them pay you! Comfortable living, dining and sitting rooms, with vaulted ceilings. Country kitchen with large windows. The large Master bedroom features an in-suite bathroom. Each bedroom has it's own bathroom located next to it. Two-car attached garage, and additional 2 carports for your toys. The drive to the main house is paved. The back yard is fenced for dogs, with shade. The landscape provides shade, a fenced garden, fruit trees, and a seasonal pond. Second- 3 bedroom house has new appliances, and is ready to be used for rental income (full lease, AIR-BNB, or VRBO). Home is set away from the main house with a gravel drive. Privacy with great views from the large front porch. Property has water spigots located throughout. Three fenced acres includes a new barn. Chicken yard with coops.Best of both worlds, independent country living and close to town. Grow your garden, raise your food or simply take a short drive into town for shopping. Located just off Highway 49, halfway between Mariposa and Oakhurst; 13 miles in either direction. Description of number of bed, bath and sqft are of both homes combined.
